ComicInfo.Series: G.I. Joe: A Real American Hero
ComicInfo.Summary: Clutch and Rock & Roll liberate three teenage prisoners in Cobra's new Rancho Cobra base, but Clutch and two of the teens wind up being recaptured and Dr. Mindbender decides to use the brainwave scanner on Clutch. The Joe team in Benzheen observes as Pale Peony, the Dreadnoks, Destro and the Baroness crash Darklon's efforts to obtain the Krytron. Unfortunately, Airtight & Dusty are captured by Benzheen authorities.
